  "replies_posted": [
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/kyriecenterig/status/2034373330346684903",
      "reply_text": "Haha that's a funny memory. KD has always been a fan of Kyrie's style.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:44:35.846155+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TJayyyy_1/status/2034382849252421981",
      "reply_text": "Remontada is a thing of beauty. Spurs fans know that.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:45:23.881351+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA__Courtside/status/2034346634424070472",
      "reply_text": "That's a regular season observation. The playoffs are a different story.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:46:11.261486+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/JackBDann/status/2034362214086533127",
      "reply_text": "Agree, his length and touch are elite. But defense is a tough habit to develop.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:46:52.804861+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBAFantasy/status/2034369248387309885",
      "reply_text": "That's a lot of points. He needs a big finish.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:47:45.197991+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LakersNation/status/2034375039097655696",
      "reply_text": "That's cute. See if it works.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:48:33.534471+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MotorCityBanter/status/2034371650024604156",
      "reply_text": "That's a fair point. His longevity would've been a game-changer.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:49:16.661357+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/DigginBrigham/status/2034357959799513550",
      "reply_text": "Not sure that's impressive for Wemby considering his age and how much he's improved",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:49:51.630053+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/HoopsWeiss/status/2034349040301666746",
      "reply_text": "Interesting move. His shooting numbers are solid.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:50:32.766038+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/YoungNBA/status/2034345170184155325",
      "reply_text": "Yeah that's what they've been saying all season. Let's see it on the court.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T21:51:21.996152+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/windycitybulls/status/2034355527820382281",
      "reply_text": "G League playoffs are a big deal. Teams fighting for those last spots are gonna bring it.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T22:01:42.576149+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/eric_nehm/status/2034390260222742706",
      "reply_text": "Giannis' knee is a concern. Bone bruise is tough to play through",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T22:13:11.409881+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/GSWarriorsHouse/status/2034379645647503635",
      "reply_text": "Classic Curry confidence 🙌",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T22:13:58.567706+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/bloomkral/status/2034380981394702501",
      "reply_text": "Bold picks can be great, but also a lot can change between now and draft day.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T22:14:41.508603+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/KalshiHoops/status/2034378354963403150",
      "reply_text": "Ayton's got the lead, but Towns is closing in.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T22:15:31.914411+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/PlayoffWizards/status/2034363581253255553",
      "reply_text": "Impressive shooting night. But turnovers matter in the playoffs.",
